threatening their mission to protect humanity.","genre_ids":[28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8007,"vote_count":886,"poster_path":"/wqfu3bPLJaEWJVk3QOm0rKhxf1A.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-01","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/fd9K7ZDfzRAcbLh8JlG4HIKbtuR.jpg","original_title":"The Old Guard 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":541671,"adult":false,"title":"Ballerina","video":false,"overview":"Taking place during the events of John Wick: Chapter 3 – Parabellum, Eve Macarro begins her training in the assassin traditions of the Ruska Roma.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.6454,"vote_count":2342,"poster_path":"/2VUmvqsHb6cEtdfscEA6fqqVzLg.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-04","vote_average":7.263,"backdrop_path":"/1yktYsxkmUtUFTUnCAUaqG6FEiz.jpg","original_title":"Ballerina","original_language":"en"},{"id":1233413,"adult":false,"title":"Sinners","video":false,"overview":"Trying to leave their troubled lives behind, twin brothers return to their hometown to start again, only to discover that an even greater evil is waiting to welcome them back.","genre_ids":[27,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":33.8352,"vote_count":3738,"poster_path":"/qTvFWCGeGXgBRaINLY1zqgTPSpn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-16","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/nAxGnGHOsfzufThz20zgmRwKur3.jpg","original_title":"Sinners","original_language":"en"},{"id":1241982,"adult":false,"title":"Moana 2","video":false,"overview":"After receiving an unexpected call from her wayfinding ancestors, Moana journeys alongside Maui and a new crew to the far seas of Oceania and into dangerous, long-lost waters for an adventure unlike anything she's ever faced.","genre_ids":[16,12,10751,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.0196,"vote_count":2934,"poster_path":"/aLVkiINlIeCkcZIzb7XHzPYgO6L.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-21","vote_average":6.995,"backdrop_path":"/zo8CIjJ2nfNOevqNajwMRO6Hwka.jpg","original_title":"Moana 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":533535,"adult":false,"title":"Deadpool & Wolverine","video":false,"overview":"A listless Wade Wilson toils away in civilian life with his days as the morally flexible mercenary, Deadpool, behind him. But when his homeworld faces an existential threat, Wade must reluctantly suit-up again with an even more reluctant Wolverine.","genre_ids":[28,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":24.5553,"vote_count":8281,"poster_path":"/8cdWjvZQUExUUTzyp4t6EDMubfO.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-24","vote_average":7.558,"backdrop_path":"/ufpeVEM64uZHPpzzeiDNIAdaeOD.jpg","original_title":"Deadpool & Wolverine","original_language":"en"},{"id":672582,"adult":false,"title":"The Deep House","video":false,"overview":"While diving in a remote French lake, a couple of YouTubers who specialise in underwater exploration videos discover a house submerged in the deep waters. What was initially a unique finding soon turns into a nightmare when they discover that the house was the scene of atrocious crimes. Trapped, with their oxygen reserves falling dangerously, they realise the worst is yet to come: they are not alone in the house.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6169,"vote_count":1078,"poster_path":"/52E0LGcMKHOO91P4j6hdHKVwITP.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-30","vote_average":6.002,"backdrop_path":"/hzPcEqyxZauvKZmUT2aJxntWPVf.jpg","original_title":"The Deep House","original_language":"en"},{"id":889737,"adult":false,"title":"Joker: Folie à Deux","video":false,"overview":"While struggling with his dual identity, Arthur Fleck not only stumbles upon true love, but also finds the music that's always been inside him.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.4043,"vote_count":2790,"poster_path":"/if8QiqCI7WAGImKcJCfzp6VTyKA.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-01","vote_average":5.397,"backdrop_path":"/AVWlQpVhpudyFsSh3OQIieHHYf.jpg","original_title":"Joker: Folie à Deux","original_language":"en"},{"id":797394,"adult":false,"title":"Secret Magic Control Agency","video":false,"overview":"