9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Old Woman with the Knife | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Aging assassin Hornclaw has seen it all, but she never expected to mentor a reckless rookie like Bullfight. As their unlikely bond deepens, cracks form in the underworld they navigate together. When Hornclaw discovers someone wants her dead, she's thrust into a deadly game of deception. With enemies closing in and trust in short supply, survival means staying sharp—both blade and mind."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/100816/the-old-woman-with-the-knife"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Old Woman with the Knife"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Aging assassin Hornclaw has seen it all, but she never expected to mentor a reckless rookie like Bullfight. As their unlikely bond deepens, cracks form in the underworld they navigate together. When Hornclaw discovers someone wants her dead, she's thrust into a deadly game of deception. With enemies closing in and trust in short supply, survival means staying sharp—both blade and mind."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/100816/the-old-woman-with-the-knife"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wbmxnsv41vsg5UEaNDlf203dOWw.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Old Woman with the Knife"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Aging assassin Hornclaw has seen it all, but she never expected to mentor a reckless rookie like Bullfight. As 